Package: trelliswork
Title: Extensions to Lattice
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Johan", "Larsson", email = "johanlarsson@outlook.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package extends lattice and latticeExtra by providing new
  high-level functions, methods for existing high-level functions, panel
  functions, and themes. The objective is to replace base plotting functions
  in order to be wholly reliant on trellis graphics in R.
Depends:
  R (>= 3.4.0),
  lattice
Imports:
  grDevices,
  grid,
  gridExtra,
  latticeExtra,
  RColorBrewer,
  stats,
  utils,
  zoo
Suggests:
  covr,
  forecast,
  knitr,
  microbenchmark,
  rmarkdown,
  testthat
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
URL: https://github.com/jolars/trelliswork
BugReports: https://github.com/jolars/trelliswork/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
